ZH: 这份合同规定了我们的商务合作条款。
EN: This contract stipulates the terms of our business cooperation.

ZH: 我们需要签署一份合同来确认这次交易。
EN: We need to sign a contract to confirm this transaction.

ZH: 请您仔细阅读合同内容后再签字。
EN: Please read the contract carefully before signing.

ZH: 合同上的日期需要在双方签字之后填写。
EN: The date on the contract needs to be filled in after both parties sign.

ZH: 我们将在合同上注明支付方式和截止日期。
EN: We will specify the payment method and deadline in the contract.

ZH: 根据合同规定，任何一方都有权提前终止合作。
EN: According to the contract, either party has the right to terminate the cooperation in advance.

ZH: 签署合同前，请确保所有条款都明确无误。
EN: Before signing the contract, please make sure all terms are clear and correct.

ZH: 合同约定了产品质量要求和交付时间。
EN: The contract stipulates the product quality requirements and delivery time.

ZH: 在合同期限内，我们需要按时完成交付。
EN: We need to complete the delivery on time within the contract period.

ZH: 如果有任何疑问，请与我们沟通并作出修改合同。
EN: If you have any questions, please communicate with us and make changes to the contract.

ZH: 我们需要最新版本的合同来更新其中的信息。
EN: We need the latest version of the contract to update the information in it.

ZH: 请您查看公司法律团队审核后的合同副本。
EN: Please review the contract copy that has been audited by the company's legal team.

ZH: 合同文件应当妥善保存，以备日后参考。
EN: The contract documents should be properly preserved for future reference.

ZH: 如有违反合同内容，我们将保留诉讼的权利。
EN: If there is a violation of the contract terms, we will reserve the right to litigation.

ZH: 合同一经签署即生效，并具有法律效力。
EN: Once the contract is signed, it will take effect and have legal force.

ZH: 请您仔细检查与本公司签订的所有合同。
EN: Please carefully check all contracts signed with our company.

ZH: 我们将送上新合同草案以便您审核。
EN: We will send a new contract draft for you to review.

ZH: 请签署完整的合同，包含所有附加条款。
EN: Please sign the complete contract, including all additional clauses.

ZH: 合同中任何未明确规定的内容均需与双方商讨。
EN: Any content not clearly stipulated in the contract needs to be discussed with both parties.

ZH: 我们的法务团队将审阅合同并提出修改建议。
EN: Our legal team will review the contract and make suggestions for amendments.
